<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">الجذر:</span>ب ز ز<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">مثال:</span>بَزَّه في المصارعة<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">الرأي:</span>مرفوضة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">السبب:</span>لأنها لم ترد بهذا المعنى في المعاجم. <a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">المعنى:</span>غلبه<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">الصواب والرتبة:</span>-بَزَّه في المصارعة <span class="c4">[فصيحة]</span> <a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">التعليق:</span>ذكرت المعاجم <span class="c2">«بزّه»</span> بمعنى غَلَبه.<span class="c5"> ومنه المثل:</span> <span class="c2">«مَنْ عَزَّ بَزَّ»</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
